categories: Category:Rulers of the Empress Teta system

nodes.text: Emperor Alor Keto was a Human male and the ruler of Empress Teta during the Galactic Civil War.

Raised in the capital city Cinnagar, Alor Keto was the ruler of Empress Teta and ruled for many decades. A weak and ineffectual leader, Keto was a puppet of the Mining Guild. During the Galactic Civil War, Keto's health was in decline.
